translation.translatedDescription:
As someone who studied cybersecurity, I really appreciate Beau‚Äôs work. He‚Äôs one of the few actually preaching security best practices in this space.

The harsh truth? Most people only care about security after something goes wrong‚Äîafter the hack, the exploit, the lost funds. If more people followed accounts like Beau‚Äôs before disaster strikes, we‚Äôd avoid so many preventable catastrophes.

So yeah, huge respect for what you‚Äôre doing. You‚Äôre out here saving people from themselves, and that‚Äôs no small feat. Keep being that white knight in a space that desperately needs more of them.
